{"tid":1186753,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母今舖我真係俾OK害撚死","createTime":"2019-06-05T06:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T09:46:21.000Z","uid":26161,"like":74,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c65f87fb7d7cde75acab72823683a2b90b1ce535","tid":1186753,"uid":26161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟暗戀咗某個同事一排 佢雖然都唔係話特別特別靚 但可能返工嗰到男多女少 所以佢顯得比較出眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁小弟好不容易鼓起勇氣 幾經辛苦終於約到女神去餐廳食飯飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等咗呢一日已經等咗好耐架啦 呢幾日仲開心到瞓唔到教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一個真男人 速度唔可以快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />紙巾一定要帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />既然約得囡囡去高級餐廳食飯 衣著當然唔可以著得咁失禮 偷著咗老竇套西裝皮鞋 gel個油頭照個鏡 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><del>雖然毒撚點搞都係柒但係</del></span>有自信既男人係最charm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今鋪女神肯定都擋唔住我既魅力 已經急不及待好想玩玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n餐飯就差唔多食完 全程氣氛都還可以接受 雖然我好多時講完野佢都無應我搞到有時deadair<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過無辦法啦鬼叫我打扮到咁charm 正常囡囡都一定怕羞唔敢講咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為紳士既我 食完飯緊係馬上掏出我褲中既紙巾俾佢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女神入心面肯定加咗我50分了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就喺呢個時候 我突然發現咗一個錦囊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再加上餐廳無啦啦響起浪漫既歌 我知道而家係表白既好機會了 人生邊有咁多巧合 機會係留俾有機會既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我直接黎個快攻拎住個錦囊向佢表白 唔知係咪因為一切黎得太突然 嚇到佢俾唔切反應 仲面紅到揜住個口話要走先 無計啦喺咁有feel既環境下我係女都心動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唯有返屋企再問佢考慮成點啦 但係結果成晚佢wtsapp都係得一個剔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都算啦點知第二日返到office俾人笑 我先發覺自己好似柒咗...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x8Q3E3z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx8Q3E3z.png&h=e886a922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母OK 到底呢啲幸運指數到底有乜撚野用 邊撚到5粒星非常好OK呀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家仲要俾啲同事笑我係ok仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪當我狗咁撚 我屌你老母呀OK！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"904e57dec3ec24917b61afe3801c672275f3e287","tid":1186753,"uid":133289,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"1分重作"},{"pid":"b207db2c152a0a4510842b861ed1271c148817d3","tid":1186753,"uid":93876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:52:41.000Z","msg":"OK占卜師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08feccd386d12dcdc3f50dfc312abf954ccf49bb","tid":1186753,"uid":26161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"904e57dec3ec24917b61afe3801c672275f3e287","tid":1186753,"uid":133289,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"1分重作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:54:26.000Z","m